snippet: Paul Casey matched the PGA Tour record for the best score on a back nine, carding an eight-under 27 in the second round at the Byron Nelson Championship in Irving, Tex.
abstract: Paul Casey cards eight-under 27 in the second round of Byron Nelson Championship, matching PGA Tour record for best score on a back nine; other golf news noted.
